	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/microsoft.md`. The file follows the same structure as `apple.md` and includes:\n\n- **Key Metrics table** with revenue, EPS (actual vs. consensus), operating metrics, and CapEx\n- **Segment Analysis** covering Intelligent Cloud (Azure +39%), Productivity & Business Processes (M365/LinkedIn/Dynamics), and More Personal Computing\n- **AI & Copilot** section with GitHub Copilot milestones, Azure AI contribution to growth, CapEx investment rationale, and OpenAI partnership context (including the equity revaluation driving the GAAP +60% net income spike)\n- **Market Reaction** addressing the Azure reacceleration as the key catalyst and analyst framing around CapEx efficiency\n- **Forward Outlook** with guidance direction and risk/opportunity framework\n- All sources from the prior findings listed" ;
