	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/created_at> "2026-03-28T14:54:39.513806+00:00" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/apple.md`.\n\nThe file covers all requested sections:\n\n- **Key Metrics** — revenue ($143.76B, +16%), EPS ($2.84 actual vs $2.67 consensus, +6.4% beat), gross margin (48.2%), OCF ($53.9B record), and a full segment table\n- **Segment Analysis** — iPhone (+23.3% to $85.3B record), Services (+13.9% to $30.0B at 76.5% margin), Mac (-6.7%), iPad (+6.3%), Wearables (-2.2%)\n- **AI & Innovation** — Apple Intelligence rollout details; specific undisclosed metrics noted as such\n- **Market Reaction** — noted as not available from public sources rather than guessing\n- **Forward Outlook** — China rebound (+37.9%), Services expansion, iPhone 17 cycle as opportunities; regulatory/geo risks flagged\n- **Sources** — all six sources from the research findings listed with URLs" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/agent_id> "1df36764-d932-43e6-bd94-53c8de009f23" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/apple.md`.\n\nThe file covers all requested sections:\n\n- **Key Metrics** — revenue ($143.76B, +16%), EPS ($2.84 actual vs $2.67 consensus, +6.4% beat), gross margin (48.2%), OCF ($53.9B record), and a full segment table\n- **Segment Analysis** — iPhone (+23.3% to $85.3B record), Services (+13.9% to $30.0B at 76.5% margin), Mac (-6.7%), iPad (+6.3%), Wearables (-2.2%)\n- **AI & Innovation** — Apple Intelligence rollout details; specific undisclosed metrics noted as such\n- **Market Reaction** — noted as not available from public sources rather than guessing\n- **Forward Outlook** — China rebound (+37.9%), Services expansion, iPhone 17 cycle as opportunities; regulatory/geo risks flagged\n- **Sources** — all six sources from the research findings listed with URLs" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "[coder] Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/apple.md`.\n\nThe f" ;
