	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/google.md`. The file follows the same structure as `apple.md` and `microsoft.md` and covers:\n\n- **Key Metrics table** — revenue, EPS actual vs. consensus, operating income/margin, net income\n- **Segment Analysis** — Search (+17%, AI Overviews context), YouTube (miss vs. $11.84B est.), Google Cloud ($17.66B +47.7%, margin 30.1%), Other Bets (Waymo $2.1B charge)\n- **AI & Innovation** — Gemini adoption, AI Overviews query-length data (3x longer), TPU Trillium deployment, $75B 2026 CapEx guidance\n- **Market Reaction** — ~7–8% after-hours decline, YouTube miss + CapEx overhang as primary drivers despite headline beats\n- **Forward Outlook** — Cloud backlog ($240B, ~2x YoY), antitrust/DOJ case, AI search competition risks, CapEx ROI uncertainty" ;
