	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Written to `/private/tmp/swarm-fresh-stocks/analysis/companies/amazon.md`.\n\nThe file follows the same structure as `apple.md` and `microsoft.md` and covers:\n\n- **Key Metrics table** with revenue, EPS (actual vs. consensus miss explanation), operating income, and full-year figures\n- **Segment Analysis** for AWS (fastest growth in 13 quarters at +24%), North America retail (margin expansion to 9.1%), International (path to profitability), and Advertising (with a note that the raw data was truncated in prior findings)\n- **AI & Infrastructure** covering CapEx rationale, Trainium2/3 sold-out status, custom silicon >$10B run rate, and Bedrock's 60% QoQ spend growth\n- **Market Reaction** calling out the Kuiper charge context for the narrow EPS miss and the AWS reacceleration as the primary catalyst\n- **Forward Outlook** with Q1 2026 guidance ranges and a balanced risks/opportunities framework including Kuiper execution risk, CapEx ROI, and retail competition" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
