	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Swarm: Research Q4 2025 earnings reports from Apple, Microsoft, Google, and Amazon, then analyze their impact on related market sectors (semiconductors, cloud, ad tech). Produce per-company summaries, sector impact reports, cross-company correlations, and an executive summary — all from publicly available data." ;
	a <https://schema.org/SwarmRun> .


